org.afplib.afplib

Interface CPC

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SF
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CPCImpl

    public interface CPC
extends SF
    A representation of the model object 'CPC'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Def Char ID
    • Prt Flags
    • CPIRG Len
    • VS Char SN
    • VS Char
    • VS Flags

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getCPC()
